{"lastModified":1768956704124,"uri":"c::8864389904::vessel::d5cc7960-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Australia\n\nCHAOS is a sophisticated 30m (98ft) Sunseeker superyacht available for an event, corporate or overnight charter in Australia. With modern interiors and a spacious sundeck, CHAOS caters for all types of events from corporate entertaining to team-building, the options are endless. With warm, soft tones throughout her interiors accompanied by entertainment screens, multiple dining spaces and a swimming platform for easy access to the ocean, CHAOS is the ultimate day charter yacht that offers a seamless experience with luxury style on the water.\n\nCHAOS is a Sunseeker yacht with a refit in 2020. She ensures a first-class charter experience for up to eight guests for an overnight charter in four spacious cabins all with ensuites, air-conditioning and TV screens. The Master cabin is a full-beam master flooded with natural light, a walk-in wardrobe and a wide-screen TV. Enjoy your own personal chef and dedicated crew to attend to your every need during your charter. Wake up to breakfast on the aft-deck with the ocean as your backdrop, hop in and out of the warm, clear waters easily with the swimming platform or relax with a sundowner at the bar on the sundeck - the choices are endless.\n","blueprint":{"name":"CHAOS","images":["/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cc7960-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yacht-image-58660-full-chaos_sydney_jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cc7960-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yacht-image-58991-full-chaos_2_jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cc7960-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yacht-image-58864-full-chaos_sydney_2_jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cc7960-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yacht-image-70074-full-1_jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::